              <text x="545" y="306" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter,system-ui" font-size="11.5" fill="#475569">sin adorno superfluo</text>
              <text x="545" y="334" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter,system-ui" font-size="11" font-style="italic" fill="#64748b">"la forma sigue a la función"</text>
